title: Blue Tile Lounge - Home Video
description: "To celebrate 25 years of their existence Blue Tile Lounge have released their brand new ‘Home’ video. Massive congrats to BTL for killing it constantly! Enjoy this belter offering below featuring the likes of Ben St. Aubin, Justin David, Evan Hay, Lee Yankou, Chris Kuitenbrouwer, Harry Brewer, Josh Bos, Dylan Barnes and Ryan DesRoches. Filmed by Devin Guiney and Daniel Policelli with editing by Rob Lane, Justin Czank and Devin Guiney. Get stuck in below! " -Vague Mag
